#include<iostream>
#include<algorithm>
using namespace std;
int main(){
	int t,n,i,count,x;
	cin>>t;
	while(t--){
		cin>>n;
		int a[n];
		for(i=0;i<n;i++)
		cin>>a[i];
		sort(a,a+n);
		x=a[0];
		for(i=0,count=0;i<n;i++){
			if(x!=a[i]){
				x=a[i];
				++count;	
			}
		}
		if((count+1)==n)
		cout<<"YES";
		else
		cout<<"NO";
		cout<<endl;
	}
	return 0;
}
